  <div class="hd">
    <h2>
      读书笔记&nbsp;&nbsp;· · · · · ·&nbsp;
          <span class="pl">(<a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/3191866/annotation">共<span property="v:count">23</span>篇</a>)</span>

    </h2>

      <a class="redbutt rr j a_show_login" href="https://www.douban.com/register?reason=annotate" rel="nofollow"><span>我来写笔记</span></a>
